entries.title_d: You've been given the task to patrol the Valarian-controlled areas surrounding Hutt Claims. Time for a little revenge! You rub your hands together evilly and cackle... at this rate, you probably look as scary as an Overkreetle. May want to work on your scariness rating.
entries.title: Tatoo System: Patrol Valarian-Controlled Areas
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast1 Hutt Informant:\#pcontrast3 < Watch your back, pilot! Valarians coming in hard and fast! >
entries.quest_patrol_d: Fly your nifty ship to designated areas sent to you by Garett.
entries.quest_location_d: Fly to the Tatoo System for your mission.
